Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
Gross Soda Challenge - Higher or Lower ► http://bit.ly/2dlEh6f

We're here in Tokyo this week, so in honor of being halfway around the world, we're streaming LIVE to share what we're doing with you and have a good ol' fashion Japanese snack-off! We're talking about Japanese gaming and trying lots of Japanese snacks that have been picked out for us to try, if we can stomach them!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive

FNAF Sister Location is HERE! ►► http://bit.ly/2dYddoA
FREAKY Frozen Games with Anna & Elsa ► http://bit.ly/GTLelsa
Don't YIFF Foxy! - Dayshift at Freddy's ► http://bit.ly/2ef6CqC

Don't have much time but need a quick fix? Check out some of our highlight episodes for hilarious moments from our live streams. Here are a few to get you started.
